reviewText: My son is 11 months old and he loves Sesame Street. But this DVD isn't one that he loves.  I think it's for older kids.  I do think that they should do an entire collection of "A Celebration of Me" for all of the Sesame Street characters. It's a very cool DVD, just not for little kids that like a lot of songs in their DVD's. There are more skits then songs. But I do recommend it.
summary: Sesame Street - A Celebration of Me, Grover
Title: N/A

reviewText: I was so happy to find this dvd.  My 2-year-old daughter has been fascinated with Grover for several months.  Funny thing, it all started with her love of Yoda.  One day we were watching Sesame Street and she perked up, running to kiss Grover on the tv, calling him Yoda.  She recognized the voice, so since then I have searched for a Grover dvd.  I finally found this one and it is so nice. Very cute, very sweet, classic Grover!  Yea!

reviewText: This item arrived before the estimated time of delivery, and was well packaged. As soon as it arrived, we tore open the package and watched the video. This is the ONLY video that my 15 mo will sit still for (or cling to the entertainment center directly in front of the TV to watch). No issues with skipping - minor scratches on disk - overall condition was good.
summary: MOST LOVED VIDEO (according to baby girl)
